newsitem.title: EU: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 285 OF NOVEMBER 7, 1996.
newsitem.headline: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ L 285 OF NOVEMBER 7, 1996.

text.p: (Note - contents are displayed in reverse order to that in the printed Journal)

Corrigendum to Decision No 4/96 of the Association Council between the European Communities and their Member States, of the one part, and the Republic of Poland, of the other part, of 16 July 1996 amending Protocol 4 concerning the definition of 'originating products' and methods of administrative cooperation (96/497/Euratom, ECSC, EC) (Official Journal of the European Communities No L 208 of 17 August 1996)

Corrigendum to Commission Regulation (EC) No 1444/96 of 24 July 1996 amending Annex I to Council Regulation (EC) No 1808/95 opening and providing for the administration of Community tariff quotas bound in GATT for certain agricultural, industrial and fisheries products and establishing the detailed provisions for adapting these quotas (Official Journal of the European Communities No L 186 of 25 July 1996)

COMMISSION DECISION of 28 October 1996 on financial aid from the Community for the operation of the Community Reference Laboratory for Classical Swine Fever, Hannover, Germany (Only the German text is authentic) (Text with EEA relevance) (96/639/EC)

COMMISSION DECISION of 25 October 1996 on applications for import licences for rice and broken rice submitted in the first five working days of October 1996 under the arrangements provided for in Council Regulation (EC) No 1522/96 (96/638/EC)
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2137/96 of 6 November 1996 establishing the standard import values for determining the entry price of certain fruit and vegetables
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2136/96 of 6 November 1996 fixing the import duties in the rice sector
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2135/96 of 6 November 1996 fixing, for October 1996, the specific agricultural conversion rate for the amount of the reimbursement of storage costs in the sugar sector

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2134/96 of 6 November 1996 amending Regulation (EC) No 3582/93 laying down detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EEC) No 2073/92 on promoting consumption in the Community and expanding the markets for milk and milk products

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2133/96 of 6 November 1996 on detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EEC) No 3483/92 laying down special measures for the transport of certain fresh fruit and vegetables originating in Greece and despatched in 1996
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2132/96 of 6 November 1996 adopting for 1997 the measures to improve the quality of olive oil production

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2131/96 of 6 November 1996 amending Regulation (EC) No 1503/96 on the detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EC) No 3072/95 with regard to import duties on rice
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2130/96 of 6 November 1996 fixing the representative prices and the additional import duties for molasses in the sugar sector

COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2129/96 of 6 November 1996 fixing the maximum export refund for white sugar for the 14th partial invitation to tender issued within the framework of the standing invitation to tender provided for in Regulation (EC) No 1464/96
COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2128/96 of 6 November 1996 fixing the export refunds on white sugar and raw sugar exported in its unaltered state END OF DOCUMENT.
